      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Verwandtachaftaweiaung für Katharina, Witwe dea Franz WulczendorJJer und Margarete,
               Witwe des Nikolaus Holczhakker</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p> 2 Einbr. 2 Zg. (Inde:x: Item frewntsehaft Klaren des Wentlinger witib) <rs
                  type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_469">(fol.78r) Desselben tages komm fur den rat <rs
                     type="fn" role="witness"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_469"
                        >Kathrein, <rs type="person" ref="#pe__franz_von_wulzendorf_StB_I_469"
                           >Franczen des Wulczendorffer</rs>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__franz_von_wulzendorf_StB_I_469"
                           >witib</roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_469"><roleName type="title">fraw</roleName>
                           Margret<roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__niklas_holzhacker_StB_I_469"
                              ><add>witib</add></roleName>, <rs type="person"
                           ref="#pe__niklas_holzhacker_StB_I_469">Niclas <roleName type="dead"
                              >witib</roleName> des <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown"
                              >Holczhakker</roleName></rs></rs>, und haben da beweist mit den erbern
                     lewten, als si ze recht solten, mit <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__ulrich_hefendlein_StB_I_469"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Ulreichen dem Hefendlein</rs> und mit <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__konrad_slosser_StB_I_469"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Chunratem dem <roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Slozzer</roleName></rs></rs>, daz <rs type="fn"
                     role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__klara_StB_I_469"><roleName
                           type="title">fraw</roleName> Clar, <rs type="person"
                           ref="#pe__peter_wentlinger_StB_I_274">Petreins des Wentlinger <roleName
                              type="dead"><add>witib</add></roleName></rs>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__peter_wentlinger_StB_I_274"
                           >witib</roleName>, drey <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_469">recht swestern</roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_469"><add>recht
                              swestern</add></roleName>gewesen sind von vater und von muter.</rs>
                     <rs type="person" ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_469"><add>Kathrein</add><roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_469"><add>recht
                           swestern</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__klara_StB_I_469"><add>recht
                        swestern</add></roleName></rs><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_469"><add>Margret</add>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_469"><add>recht
                              swestern</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__klara_StB_I_469"><add>recht
                     swestern</add></roleName></rs></rs> Als darumb die obgenanten erbern lewt vor
                  offem rat an aydes stat gesagt habent, als si ze recht solten.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
